title: How to Paint Tomb Kings Of Khemri Tomb Guard
description:
In this video, we'll be showing you how to paint a Tomb Kings of Khemri, Tomb Guard Champion. Once they're Battle Ready, we'll show you a how to do a few more steps to take it to the next level!

If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started
